<subSubSection id="C368652E93508E0DF2AAFF4DFAADFED6" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593508E0DF2AAFF4DFAADFED6" blockId="9.[151,1436,223,430]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">
<materialsCitation id="3B1A3CF893508E0DF2AAFF4DFAA9FED6" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3798147334" collectionCode="R" collectorName="P. Pantel &amp; J. Serrano" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" specimenCount="2" typeStatus="lectotype">
The specimen here designated as 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793508E0DF025FF4DFDAEFF32" box="[536,639,223,249]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">lectotype</typeStatus>
is a male bearing the labels: “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693508E0DF1E2FF4DFBF9FF32" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[991,1064,223,249]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="similis">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793508E0DF1E2FF4DFBF9FF32" box="[991,1064,223,249]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">similis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in Dalmatia”, “ex-Museo Chaudoir”, “ 
<collectionCode id="ED63AE6093508E0DF2D7FE91FED1FED6" box="[234,256,259,285]" country="Chile" name="Departamento de Geologia, Universidad de Chile" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">R</collectionCode>
. 
<collectorName id="2687537393508E0DF33EFE91FEBBFED6" box="[259,362,259,285]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">P. Pantel</collectorName>
”, “Pater.” and “ 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793508E0DF02AFE91FD5BFED6" box="[535,650,259,285]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">Lectotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693508E0DF08DFE91FB54FED6" authority="Dejean, 1829" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[688,1157,259,285]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="similis" subGenus="Ophonus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793508E0DF08DFE91FC39FED6" box="[688,1000,259,285]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">Harpalus (Ophonus) similis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493508E0DF1D2FE91FB54FED6" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[1007,1157,259,285]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean, 1829</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
desig. by 
<collectorName id="2687537393508E0DF6C5FE96FABFFED6" box="[1272,1390,259,286]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">J. Serrano</collectorName>
”
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C368652E93508E0DF2FAFEB5FB23FE66" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593508E0DF2FAFEB5FBB6FE8A" blockId="9.[151,1436,223,430]" box="[199,1127,295,321]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493508E0DF2FAFEB5FEB9FE8A" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[199,360,295,321]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean (1829)</bibRefCitation>
briefly stated: 
<emphasis id="B906EAB793508E0DF02CFEB5FBB6FE8A" box="[529,1127,295,321]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">
Il se trouve en Dalmatie et dans le midi de la 
<collectingCountry id="F365763593508E0DF632FEBAFBB2FE8A" box="[1039,1123,296,321]" name="France" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">France</collectingCountry>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593508E0DF2FAFED9FD2AFE41" blockId="9.[151,1436,223,430]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">
This species is well distinguishable from related taxa (
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493508E0DF11AFED9FC17FEAE" author="Jeannel, R." box="[807,966,331,357]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" pagination="572 - 1173" refId="ref11231" refString="Jeannel, R. (1942) Coleopteres carabiques. Deuxieme partie. Faune de France 40. Librairie de la Faculte des Sciences, Paris, pp. 572 - 1173." type="book chapter" year="1942">Jeannel, 1942</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493508E0DF1ECFED9FBB4FEAE" author="Sciaky, R." box="[977,1125,331,357]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" pagination="29 - 120" refId="ref12184" refString="Sciaky, R. (1987) Revisione delle specie paleartiche occidentali del genere Ophonus Dejean, 1821. Memoria della Societa Entomologica Italiana, 65, 29 - 120." type="journal article" year="1987">Sciaky, 1987</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493508E0DF64DFEDEFB2CFEAE" author="Wrase, D. W." box="[1136,1277,331,358]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" refId="ref12634" refString="Wrase, D. W. (2011) Genus Tschitscherinellus. Arndt, E., Schnitter, P., Sfenthourakis, S. &amp; Wrase, D. W. (Eds.), Ground beetles (Carabidae) of Greece. Pensoft, Sofia, pp. 163." type="book" year="2011">Wrase, 2011</bibRefCitation>
) due to dorsal colouration, punctures on the striae, apex of penis, etc.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593508E0DF2FAFE06FB23FE66" blockId="9.[151,1436,223,430]" box="[199,1266,403,430]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">
It is distributed in Central and Mediterranean Europe and the Levant (
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493508E0DF1E9FE01FB37FE66" author="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W." box="[980,1254,403,430]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" pagination="1810" refId="ref11718" refString="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W. (2017 c) Subtribe Harpalina Bonelli, 1810. In: Lobl, I. &amp; Lobl, D. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera. Vol. 1. Revised and Updated Edition. Brill, Leiden, pp. 515 - 562." type="book chapter" year="2017">Kataev &amp; Wrase, 2017c</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
